    <text>
        <body>
            <div>
                <head>Translated parts</head>
                <p xml:id="KR3a0014-start">
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:10.986+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:14.152+09:00">'‘圆形的物体易动，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:20.984+09:00">方形的物体易静,</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-1a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:21.824+09:00">这体现了天地的本质呀!"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:45.366+09:00">文中子说:"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:52.348+09:00">睿智者快乐，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:34:56.851+09:00">是因为他心中可包容万物。</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:35:07.988+09:00">仁爱者长寿，</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-2a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:03.555+09:00">是因为他忘却自我私欲。"</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.2" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:14.929+09:00">文中子说:</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.3" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:19.221+09:00">''姚义，清素而端庄；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.4" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:23.566+09:00">李靖，惠物而勇断；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.5" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:27.951+09:00">窦威，和容而博识；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.6" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:36:31.629+09:00">薛收,体旷而志肃；</seg>
                    <seg corresp="#KR3a0014_tls_002-3a.7" xml:lang="en" resp="#CH" modified="2024-12-05T07:37:01.369+09:00">贾琼,通明而果毅;杜淹,诚意而威厉;房玄龄，志精而用密；魏征，直道而遂行；温大雅，量深而宽宏；陈叔达,简静而中正。这些人如遇良机，官职不会低于卿相，然而礼乐方面却不完备。”</seg>
                </p>
            </div>
